，算投资回报。如果这里面发生了严重偏差，实际产出的芯片就难以赢得市场。","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":2476436,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/25/c9/94/43dbbd2c.jpg","nickname":"Winnie.S","note":"","ucode":"2BD50725236956","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":520538,"discussion_content":"可以加10分钟的回复 ：）","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1621837611,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":294158,"user_name":"springXu","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2064750,"ip_address":"","ucode":"F5DB0B963C894F","user_header":"","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1621801416,"is_pvip":true,"replies":[{"id":"106747","content":"其实Intel的设计能力也很不错的。","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"Winnie.S","uid":"2476436","ctime":1621840493,"ip_address":"","comment_id":294158,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"1621801416","product_id":100079201,"comment_content":"在这个问题上，我认为是具体问题具体分析的。也就是说在某些项目中需求分析相对于其他环节是最重要的，在某些项目中需求分析却不一定比其他环节最重要的。<br>例子如下，MTK在功能机上一站式服务的手机解决方案来说，MTK的芯片设计的需求分析是到位的。 因为原来这种解决方案像IT和飞利浦的手机芯片，必然会有像龙旗这样的方案公司出现。MTK手机方案是解决一整套，它的需求分析就是做的好。<br>但像Intel Larrabee项目，需求是显卡一切都用可编程性来解决。最后发现显卡不能完全用软件来实现。这个不是需求分析没做好吧。<br>还是intel对于它自身有自己的晶圆厂，它的生产工艺达不到它的设计水平了，再强的需求分析，生产工艺达不到必然也没下文了。题外话，苹果看中intel，选用intel就是它的生产工艺比别家强一代半的时间。","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":2476436,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/25/c9/94/43dbbd2c.jpg","nickname":"Winnie.S","note":"","ucode":"2BD50725236956","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":520536,"discussion_content":"其实Intel的设计能力也很不错的。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1621840493,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]}]}